Class AbstractTopology

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.labs.samoa.topology.AbstractTopology
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Topology
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    S4Topology, SamzaTopology, SimpleTopology, StormTopology, ThreadsTopology

    public abstract class AbstractTopology
extends Object
implements Topology
    Topology abstract class. It manages basic information of a topology: name, sets of Streams and ProcessingItems
